gitCommit.subject: refactor(app): move breadcrumb navigation into header, adjust header layout and styling, rename bundled assets
gitCommit.body:
refactor(app): move breadcrumb navigation into header, adjust header layout and styling, rename bundled assets

- Updated `App.module.css` to introduce `.headerLeft` (flex layout), reduce header padding, add min‑height, and refine breadcrumb styling (spacing, colors, overflow handling) for both desktop and mobile.
- Modified `App.tsx` to render breadcrumbs inside the new header left area, removing the duplicate breadcrumb block from the main content.
- refactor(app): reduce header padding and gaps, tighten title input padding, and add left padding to mobile header for better layout after breadcrumb move.

gitCommit.body:
refactor(app): move breadcrumb navigation into header, adjust header layout and styling, rename bundled assets

- Updated `App.module.css` to introduce `.headerLeft` (flex layout), reduce header padding, add min‑height, and refine breadcrumb styling (spacing, colors, overflow handling) for both desktop and mobile.
- Modified `App.tsx` to render breadcrumbs inside the new header left area, removing the duplicate breadcrumb block from the main content.
- refactor(app): reduce header padding and gaps, tighten title input padding, and add left padding to mobile header for better layout after breadcrumb move.
